<%# src/views/partials/heart.ejs — the brand ORNAMENT (functional Material
    glyphs elsewhere, e.g. the how-to-play "Vote" rule or a photo's like
    button, are separate UI icons, not this — see src/views/feed.ejs's own
    .like-heart, which never routes through this partial and stays a heart
    in both variants, AC3). A heart for the wedding instance; the Material
    Symbols "local_bar" martini glass for the black-tie "Stag Master"
    bachelor-party variant (issue #640) — the SINGLE owner of the ornament
    swap, so every call site (masthead, admin brand, message-card pages)
    gets the martini for free without its own conditional. %>
